"title": "5440: perjury",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5440",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Swearing falsely, usually in a legal context, either by taking a false oath or by breaking one's oath later. God hates perjury.</p>\n<h2>God hates perjury</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:16-Zech8:17\">ZEC 8:16–8:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:1\">ISA 48:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:2\">JER 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:9-Jer7:10\">JER 7:9–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:4\">HOS 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:3-Zech5:4\">ZEC 5:3–5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:9-1Tim1:10\">1TI 1:9–1:10</a></p>\n<h2>The Law forbade perjury</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:16\">EXO 20:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:20\">DEU 5:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:1-Exod23:3\">EXO 23:1–23:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:12\">LEV 19:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num30:2\">NUM 30:2</a></p>\n<h2>Punishment for perjury</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:1-Lev6:7\">LEV 6:1–6:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:16-Deut19:21\">DEU 19:16–19:21</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of perjury</h2>\n<h3>Against Naboth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:1-1Kgs21:19\">1KI 21:1–21:19</a></p>\n<h3>Against Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:59-Matt26:61\">MAT 26:59–26:61</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:55-Mark14:59\">MRK 14:55–14:59</a></p>\n<h3>Against Stephen</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:12-Acts6:14\">ACT 6:12–6:14</a></p>",
